The Topps Company, Inc. All Rights Reserved.

Catalyst Game Labs and the Catalyst Game Labs logo are trademarks of
InMediaRes Productions, LLC.

This project was created under Microsoft's "Game Content Usage Rules" for
electronic BattleTech games, and is not endorsed by or affiliated with Microsoft.

This project is an unofficial, fan-created tool and is not affiliated with,
endorsed by, or licensed by Microsoft Corporation, The Topps Company, Inc.,
or Catalyst Game Labs.

## Non-Commercial Use Only

Due to the CC-BY-NC-SA-4.0 licensing of derived game data and assets, this project
as a whole cannot be used for commercial purposes when incorporating those materials.

**What is NOT permitted:**

- Commercial army builders or unit construction apps
- Subscription-based services using the game data
- Paid apps or databases built on MegaMek data
- Monetized websites hosting unit statistics or game data

**What IS permitted:**

- Personal and community non-commercial use
- Educational purposes
- Content creation about the project (streaming, videos, tutorials with monetization)
- Contributions to this open-source project

## Streams & Content Creators

Following MegaMek's policy, we explicitly grant permission for content creators to
monetize videos and streams featuring this application. This includes ads, donations,
subscriptions, sponsorships, and platform partner programs.

The key distinction: you're monetizing your creative work about the application
(commentary, tutorials, entertainment), not the game data itself.

## Contributing

By contributing to this project, you agree that:

- Code contributions will be licensed under Apache 2.0
- Data and asset contributions derived from MegaMek will be licensed under CC-BY-NC-SA-4.0
- Original data and assets you create will be clearly marked and may use Apache 2.0

## Questions

If you have questions about licensing, please open an issue in the repository.

